Problem: Customer Attrition

Solution 1: Predict Churn. Customer Retention costs less than customer acquisition. Measure effectiveness of customer retention tactic. Estimating savings. 
Solution 2: 

Solution 1: Survey customers who have already left. It is very unlikely to get a customer back once they have made the choice to leave.
This tactic will not improve customer retention but it can help us understand why customers left.

